		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The vectors are all $FFFF, FCEUltra's debugger and memory viewer showed me that pretty quickly.  I see you're using nesasm, it's just not working as one would expect.  I think you only need to put another .bank command before you do the .org $FFFA.

		

