		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I now have a new problem. For some reason, my joypad-reading routine always shows that A is pressed (#%10000000). Why? Newest build available <a href="http://www.geocities.com/doubledistelfink/tictactoe.zip" class="postlink">here.</a>

		

